    Task

    Explore Solutions and Conduct Research

    As a researcher, I explore solutions for scientific research, so that I can find relevant information and evidence for my studies.

    Success definition: Given I am on the Epsilon AI homepage and the Solutions menu is available When I click on the Solutions button and select Scientific Research, followed by entering a research question in the search box Then I should see the solutions related to Scientific Research displayed, and the search box should be populated with the question 'What are the common genetic targets used for treating lung cancer?'

    https://www.epsilon-ai.com/

        StaticText AI
    paragraph
        StaticText For each search query, Epsilon finds the top 100 related papers and passes them along with your query to GPT-4 to generate a summary of the scientific information. Because it uses citations to academic literature, Epsilon is a factual and trustworthy way to use AI for your research.
